765
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:06,466
- [grunts]

766
00:32:06,508 --> 00:32:09,469
- [grunting]

767
00:32:09,511 --> 00:32:11,096
[yells]

768
00:32:11,137 --> 00:32:13,390
[glass shattering]
- [grunting]

769
00:32:13,432 --> 00:32:14,725
[whoosh]

770
00:32:14,767 --> 00:32:16,351
<i>♪ ♪</i>

771
00:32:16,393 --> 00:32:18,645
- She okay?
- She's gonna be okay, yeah.

772
00:32:18,687 --> 00:32:20,856
Do you have any more ideas?

773
00:32:20,898 --> 00:32:22,065
- Where do I breach him?

774
00:32:22,107 --> 00:32:23,483
- Ramon, no, you...

775
